    "created_at": "2016-02-04T21:54:49Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-02-04T21:54:49Z",
    "body": "> but how I would send mouse events?\n\nYou can simulate mouse events withs something like the following:\n\n``` js\nvar mouseMove = new MouseEvent('mousemove', {\n  view: window,\n  bubbles: true,\n  clientX: 256\n});\ndocument.body.dispatchEvent(mouseMove);\n```\n\nhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MouseEvent\n\nI'm going to close this out. If you need more help or want to discuss this further, I'd recommend posting a thread over on the message forum, https://discuss.atom.io/c/electron\n"
